{"word":"κατεπείγω","slug":"κατεπείγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατεπείγω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to press down, depress</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to press much, press hard, drive on, urge on, impel</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to hasten, make haste</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}